'''Buti''' ({{lang-en|Bear}}; {{lang-ar|п»пе}})  waa [[xayawaan]] aad u wany oo [[duurjoog]] ah, taas oo ka mid ah xayawaanka [[naasley]]da ah.
Butidu waxay u eegtahay [[ey]]ga waana [[hilibcun]], [[ugaadhsi|ugaadhsata]] [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[dad]]ka iyo [[kaluun]]ka. 

Butidu waa [[xayawaan]] ku nool [[dhul]]ka [[cimilo|cimilada]] qaboow leh ee [[joog|jooga sareeya]] sida [[buur]]aha. Waxayna u badan tahay [[qaarad]]aha [[Koonfur Ameerika]], [[Waqooyiga Ameerika]], [[Yurub]], [[Aasiya]] iyo [[cidhif|labada cidhif]] ee [[dhul]]ka. 

Guud ahaan, butidu waxay leedahay [[jidh]] wayn, [[lug|labo lugood]] oo awood badan, [[labo|labo gacmood]] oo [[cidi]]yo dhaadheer, [[af]] soo taagan oo [[ilig|shan miciyood]] ku yaalaan iyo [[timo]] [[dhogor]] badan oo ku dahaaran jidhka. 

[[San]]ka Butidu waa mid meel dheer wax ka [[ur]]in kara. Sidoo kale, butidu waa xayawaan adkeysi badan u leh [[qaboow]]ga ayadoo '''Butida Cad''' eey ku nooshahay [[cidhif]]yada [[dhul]]ka. 

Inkastoo noocyo badan oo butida ka mid ah tafiir go'een, maanta waxaa jira sideed nooc oo buti ah kuna kala nool daafaha dhulka. 
